		<node ID="ID_289606868" LINK="https://rubygarage.org/blog/technology-stack-for-web-development" TEXT="Web Application Development Technology Stack in 2020">
			<node ID="ID_654848041" TEXT="Altogether these technologies help us deliver products faster and keep high quality. Depending on your business needs we can rework a technology stack for instance add necessary libraries or frameworks. Below you can find our choice for both frontend and backend web app development. The Technology Stack at RubyGarage" />
